      "activity_c": [
        {
          "id": "t_1_1",
          "text": "My name is Kamal. I am a trainee at the Sri Lankan–German Training Institute.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_1.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_2",
          "text": "I study the training modules in the morning and in the afternoon.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_2.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_3",
          "text": "From Monday to Friday, I follow a routine with my classmates.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_3.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_4",
          "text": "We start the training at eight o’clock.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_4.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_5",
          "text": "In the morning, I meet my friends and we talk for a few minutes.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_5.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_6",
          "text": "Then we go to the workshop.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_6.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_7",
          "text": "I use different tools, and I practise with equipment.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_7.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_8",
          "text": "Sometimes I measure materials, sometimes I check machines, and sometimes I observe simple experiments.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_8.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_9",
          "text": "We listen to the instructor and we ask questions.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_9.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_10",
          "text": "The teacher explains the lesson step by step.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_10.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_11",
          "text": "Sometimes the instructor gives us a group project, and we must share our ideas and responsibilities.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_11.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_12",
          "text": "We have a tea break from ten thirty to eleven o’clock.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_12.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_13",
          "text": "We sit together, we drink tea, and we eat short eats.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_13.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_14",
          "text": "After the break, I continue my work.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_14.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_15",
          "text": "I read instructions, I do small projects and I write notes in my exercise book.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_15.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_16",
          "text": "We often work in pairs or in groups.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_16.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_17",
          "text": "I also use the computer to practise ICT skills.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_17.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_18",
          "text": "When I practise on the computer, I learn new software that is useful for our future careers.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_18.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_19",
          "text": "At noon we go for lunch.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_19.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_20",
          "text": "In the afternoon, we learn safety rules, practise English sentences, and play a short learning game.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_20.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_21",
          "text": "We do not sleep in class, and we do not waste time.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_21.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_22",
          "text": "Sometimes the teacher asks us to present our work, and this helps us build confidence in speaking English.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_22.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_23",
          "text": "At the end of the day, I clean my tools and I tidy the workshop.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_23.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_24",
          "text": "Before we leave, we discuss the next day’s plan, so everyone knows what to prepare in advance.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_24.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_1_25",
          "text": "We leave the institute at four fifteen.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_1_25.mp3"
        }
      ],
